'''''Panchira''''', (パンチラ) waa kelmad Jabaaniis ah oo tilmaamaysa aragti kooban oo ah nigiska dumarka.  Ereyga wuxuu xambaarsan yahay tilmaamo halis ah oo la mid ah erayga '[[darafyada hoostooda]]' oo Ingiriis ah.

Ee [[anime]] iyo [[manga]], ''panchira'' caadiyan waxaa loola jeedaa panty-shot, shir muuqaal ah oo ay si weyn u adeegsadeen fannaaniinta Jabaan iyo kuwa nooleyaasha ah ilaa horraantii 1960-meeyadii. Sida laga soo xigtay ilo-wareedyo Jabaan ah, shirku wuxuu u badan yahay inuu ku billowday fanaankii caanka ahaa ee Machiko Hasegawa ee ''[[Sazae-san]]'', kaas oo qaab-dhismeedkiisa dabeecadda Wakame Isono uu ku daray xad-dhaaf aan macquul ahayn.<ref>Akihara, Koji, and Takekuma, Kentaro. ''Even a Monkey Can Draw Manga.'' VIZ Media LLC; 1st edition, 2002.</ref>  Dhaqanka ayaa markii dambe loo wareejiyay animation markii Osamu Tezuka oo ''[[Astro Boy]]'' loo habeeyay telefishanka 1963.<ref>Koji and Takekuma, ''Even a Monkey Can Draw Manga.''</ref> Laga soo bilaabo markaa, panchira waxay la xiriirtay kaftan galmo sida nooca laga helo majaajillo badan ''[[shōnen manga]]''.<ref>Millegan, Kris. "Sex in Manga", ''Comics Journal,'' 1999.</ref>

